reviewText: Not one, not two, but three fabulous Cindarella stories in one package... It was almost too much for our princess-mad child to endure! This is a perfect gift for girls of any age, even us girls of a certain age. Warning to parents: Be aware that you may find yourself watching these Cindarella stories over and over again. You may also find yourself enjoying it as much as the younger girls do.Lots of fun and recommended for family viewing.
